The open source community is very important to Sourcefire and we welcome your feedback. The Snort Team, VRT, and others at Sourcefire monitor the [Snort mailing lists](http://www.snort.org/community/mailing-lists) and IRC channel. (#Snort on Freenode) Questions and comments about Snort should be submitted to one of these channels so the entire community can benefit.  Feedback on Snort.org can be sent directly to Sourcefire at [snort-site@sourcefire.com](snort-site@sourcefire.com).
